{
  "page": "House Hook",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold\">House Hook</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\"><div></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Head</th><td>\nExtinct</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Region</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">Riverlands</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/River_king\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"River king\">River king</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>House Hook</b> was a noble house of the <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">riverlands</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Hook&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The Hooks were <a href=\"/index.php/River_king\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"River king\">river kings</a> of old who once claimed the mouth of the <a href=\"/index.php/Blackwater_Rush\" title=\"Blackwater Rush\">Blackwater Rush</a> in the days of the <a href=\"/index.php/Hundred_Kingdoms\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Hundred Kingdoms\">Hundred Kingdoms</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> It is unknown if they were of <a href=\"/index.php/First_Men\" title=\"First Men\">First Men</a> or <a href=\"/index.php/Andal\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal\">Andal</a> ancestry.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headli